SUCCESS IS NO MYSTERY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 "Matlock" (ABC), "Murder, She Wrote" (CBS) and "Diagnosis Murder" (CBS): What 
do they all have in common? Writers who don't have to resort to sex and 
violence every week to put on a good program. 
</P>
