<HEADLINE>
<P>
FAREWELL TO KUCHEL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 As a lifelong Democrat, I was saddened to hear of the death of former U.S. 
Sen. Thomas H. Kuchel, as he was the last Republican legislator I ever voted 
for.Unlike today's crop, Tom Kuchel was a human being first, a gentleman next 
and a politician last. In casting my ballot it didn't matter what party Tom 
belonged to, I knew he would govern for all the people. He must have been 
thoroughly sickened by what has been taking place on both sides of the 
legislative aisle over the past decade or so. 
</P>
<P>
 To Tom Kuchel's family, take heart. He may have been the last good politician 
we will see for quite a while. 
</P>
<P>
 JERRY L. DAVIS 
</P>
<P>
 Brea 
