 Ventura improved to 6-1. 
</P>
<P>
 In the final of the Cuesta tournament: 
</P>
<P>
 Cuesta 69, Orange Coast 57 -- Jamie Shine scored 17 points and America Robledo 
added 16 for Orange Coast (9-2). The Pirates hurt themselves by making only 
five of 16 free throws. 
</P>
<P>
 In a College of the Sequoias tournament consolation game: 
</P>
<P>
 Golden West 82, College of the Canyons 70 -- Julie Murdent scored 30 points 
and had 12 rebounds for Golden West (8-3). 
