<TEXT>
<P>
 Tina Thompson had 21 points and 17 rebounds, both game highs, Saturday to lead 
24th-ranked USC to a 75-71 victory over UC Santa Barbara at the Sports Arena. 
</P>
<P>
 Thompson was six of 10 from the field and nine of 11 from the line for USC 
(2-1).Karleen Shields added 17 points for the Trojans. 
</P>
<P>
