<P>
 Rob Fulton has been appointed regional vice president for Security Life, 
responsible for operations in Orange County and the San Diego area. Fulton 
joined Security Life, a Denver-based insurance company, as assistant vice 
president of its employer-sponsored plans. Last year, he was appointed vice 
president for ING America Life's Business Insurance Operations, a Security Life 
affiliate. Rob Fulton 
