<HEADLINE>
<P>
A LITTLE BIT OF HISTORY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Eric Reynolds of Camarillo High won the Kinney national cross-country title in 
1982 after placing third in 1981. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA120494-0261 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 104874 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
December 4, 1994, Sunday, Valley Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 13; Column 4 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
