<P>
COMMUNITY NEWS: SOUTHWEST: BALDWIN HILLS; HEALTH FAIR TO OFFER FREE TESTS, 
SCREENINGS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Mainland Consulting Group is holding a health fair at 2:30 p.m. Friday at 
Baldwin Villa Plaza, 3939 Marlton Ave. 
</P>
<P>
 All services at the fair are free. Health professionals from several fields 
will offer flu shots, information and counseling on substance abuse prevention, 
cancer prevention and stress management. Screenings for prostate cancer, 
glucose levels, blood pressure and dental health will also be available. 
Participants can enjoy a health-conscious buffet and receive free cookbooks as 
well. 
</P>
<P>
 Information: (213) 747-3114. 
