Holiday Album, Kenny G (1) 10 2 Hell Freezes Over, The Eagles (3) 1 3 Unplugged 
in New York, Nirvana (5) 2 4 II, Boyz II Men (2) 3 5 Best Of, Sade (15) 4 6 
Merry Christmas, Mariah Carey (4) 15 7 Bootleg & B-Sides, Ice Cube (19) -- 8 
